Require the GAD Focal Person to observe compliance with the submission of the copy of GAD Plan and Budget to the DILG Regional Office on or before March of the preceding year for appropriate review and approval. DILG-approved GPB must include a certificate of approval from the DILG Regional Office and must be incorporated in the year’s annual budget to be enacted by the Sanggunian. Also, GAD Accomplishment Report for CY 2020 must be submitted immediately to the Provincial Government for the required review and consolidation; 

