The City Accountant to prepare BRS of the LBP Account 0202-0028-97 as of December 31, 2020 to ascertain accuracy and correctness of the Cash in Bank account and thereby adjust reconciling items in the books such as paid disbursements in the amount of ₱3,427,933.40 as noted in this observation;

In the ensuing years, the City Accountant to prepare BRS monthly and in a timely manner and submit the same to the audit team; and

The City Accountant to assess the necessity for additional manpower, for approval of the Head of Agency and the Sanggunian, to facilitate necessary financial reports.

