Direct the Barangay Officials to report to Building Official monthly/quarterly the on-going construction and completed structures in their barangays in order to assist the Building Official in monitoring compliance of the structures with the National Building Code of the Philippines and maximize income generated therewith; 

Enjoin the City Engineer to religiously monitor newly constructed buildings, whether commercial or residential; and 




Direct the City Assessor to verify whether real properties within the City are properly listed in the assessment rolls specifically those newly constructed or renovated

