review the lapsing schedule and re-compute for the correct depreciation taking into consideration the PPEs’ proper classification and the appropriate rate for the residual value;
record any changes as adjustments in the ensuing year to reflect the correct balance of accumulated depreciation for each item of PPE; and
prospectively, record the depreciation expense of the LGU’s assets to establish its correct value in the books.

