direct the Municipal Treasurer and the Municipal Accountant to work together in the preparation of the certified statement of SEF income to properly establish a more realistic basis of the available fund for appropriation;
require the LSB to submit explanation and submit support with regard to the varying and inconsistent changes of PAPs with respect to the amount of ₱181,000.00 allotted for Trainings/Incentives and awards for performing school heads and teachers; and
remind the LSB to review the budget and its components to ensure that the fund will be utilized for priority programs and projects and will be prepared in accordance with the requirements of the relevant laws, and regulations.

We recommended that Management:
