Prepare the SEF Budget in accordance with the prescribed format using Income and Expenditure Estimates Report to provide a more accurate amount that should be appropriated for SEF;
Require that the purchases of supplies and materials for distribution to recipient schools be properly documented;
Ensure that the prescribed planning and budgeting tools are effectively utilized to attain optimal and timely SEF budget; and
Strictly conform with the timelines in the planning and budgeting process as prescribed with DepEd, DBM & DILG Joint Circular No. 2017-01.

