ensure that checks issued are supported with the signatures of the claimants in the check register which will be the basis of transmittal of Disbursement Vouchers to the Accounting Office.  Moreover, unsigned “Received by” column of the check register together with the actual check not yet released will be the basis in the preparation of List of Unreleased Checks for a given period to be submitted to the Accounting Office; and
